<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 00:49:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国房地产危机刺激需求，重组专家增加香港员工</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/restructuring-specialists-boost-hong-kong-staff-china-property-crisis-stokes-2024-02-26/</link><description>随着中国的房地产危机导致债务重组交易激增，全球重组专家 Alvarez &amp;amp; Marsal 和 Houlihan Lokey 增加了在香港的员工数量，使其成为香港金融业招聘中罕见的亮点。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 23:28:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/restructuring-specialists-boost-hong-kong-staff-china-property-crisis-stokes-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>巴西BRF结束七连败，扭亏为盈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazils-brf-ends-seven-quarter-losing-streak-earns-16526-million-q4-2024-02-26/</link><description>根据周一的财报，巴西家禽和猪肉加工商 BRF SA 在 2023 年最后三个月实现利润 8.23 亿雷亚尔（1.6526 亿美元），结束了连续七个季度的亏损。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 23:02:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazils-brf-ends-seven-quarter-losing-streak-earns-16526-million-q4-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议院小组就中国药明康德和华大基因法案举行听证会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-senate-panel-sets-hearing-chinas-wuxi-apptec-bgi-bill-2024-02-26/</link><description>美国参议院小组周一表示，将于 3 月 6 日就一项法案举行听证会，该法案将禁止联邦机构与中国华大基因、无锡药明康德和其他受关注的生物技术公司签订合同。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 22:59:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/us-senate-panel-sets-hearing-chinas-wuxi-apptec-bgi-bill-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国称中国航空公司可将美国航班增加至每周 50 班</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinese-passenger-airlines-can-increase-number-us-flights-usdot-2024-02-26/</link><description>美国运输部周一表示，从 3 月 31 日起，中国客运航空公司将被允许将每周往返美国的航班从目前的 35 班增加到 50 班，使市场恢复到疫情前水平的约三分之一。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 22:23:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinese-passenger-airlines-can-increase-number-us-flights-usdot-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>古巴顶级雪茄制造商因高端需求蓬勃发展而创下销售纪录</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/cubas-top-cigar-maker-smokes-sales-record-booming-high-end-demand-2024-02-26/</link><description>古巴顶级雪茄制造商哈伯纳斯周一表示，其2023年销售额已飙升至创纪录的7.21亿美元，该公司高管将这一基准归因于中国等市场对其最豪华、高端雪茄的需求旺盛。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 22:16:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/cubas-top-cigar-maker-smokes-sales-record-booming-high-end-demand-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日本两年来首次通胀低于预期？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-26/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 21:46:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>国际原子能机构文件称，伊朗浓缩铀库存减少至60%，但问题依然存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-uranium-stock-enriched-60-shrinks-problems-persist-iaea-papers-say-2024-02-26/</link><description>联合国核监督机构周一的报告称，伊朗的接近武器级的浓缩铀库存已经减少，使其低于可以生产三颗原子弹的理论阈值，但检查人员的问题仍然存在。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 18:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/irans-uranium-stock-enriched-60-shrinks-problems-persist-iaea-papers-say-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>独家：财政部称美国对银行的警告减缓了俄罗斯的资金流动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/treasury-says-us-warning-banks-slows-russia-financial-flows-2024-02-26/</link><description>美国财政部副部长沃利·阿德耶莫表示，华盛顿威胁对外国金融机构实施制裁，这对俄罗斯与土耳其、阿拉伯联合酋长国和哈萨克斯坦等国之间的资金流动产生了重大影响。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 17:34:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/treasury-says-us-warning-banks-slows-russia-financial-flows-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>发言人称美国商会会长本周将访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-chamber-commerce-chief-visiting-china-this-week-spokesperson-says-2024-02-26/</link><description>该组织表示，美国商会首席执行官苏珊·克拉克本周将率领一个由前美国政府官员组成的代表团访问北京。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 17:22:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-chamber-commerce-chief-visiting-china-this-week-spokesperson-says-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国在阿布扎比会谈中对美国关税和台湾问题表达“严重”关切</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-expresses-solemn-concerns-over-us-tariffs-taiwan-abu-dhabi-talks-2024-02-26/</link><description>中国商务部部长王文涛周一在会见美国贸易代表戴凯时表达了中国对美国关税和涉台经贸领域问题的“严重关切”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 14:37:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-expresses-solemn-concerns-over-us-tariffs-taiwan-abu-dhabi-talks-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国最新的长征火箭将在创纪录的任务年首次亮相</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-latest-long-march-rocket-debut-year-record-missions-2024-02-26/</link><description>据官方媒体周一报道，中国的长征十二号能够将更大、功能更多的卫星送入地球轨道，预计将于 2024 年首次飞行，今年是中国发射任务创纪录的一年。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 13:23:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-latest-long-march-rocket-debut-year-record-missions-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>随着券商开始关注中国需求，亚玛芬体育股价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/amer-sports-jumps-brokerages-start-coverage-with-eye-china-demand-2024-02-26/</link><description>周一，Amer Sports 股价上涨 3.5%，分析师开始给予基本看涨评级，并强调中国市场对威尔逊网球拍制造商的优质户外和运动服装产品的强劲需求。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 12:43:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/amer-sports-jumps-brokerages-start-coverage-with-eye-china-demand-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，印度考虑对低品位铁矿石征收出口税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-considers-export-tax-low-grade-iron-ore-sources-say-2024-02-26/</link><description>两名直接参与此事的消息人士称，在小型钢铁生产商敦促政府限制其海外销售后，印度正在考虑对低品位铁矿石征收出口税。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 12:27:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-considers-export-tax-low-grade-iron-ore-sources-say-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国竞争对手的扩张，雷诺在日内瓦的欧洲电动汽车防御中处于领先地位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/renault-leads-europes-ev-defence-geneva-chinese-rivals-expand-2024-02-26/</link><description>雷诺和中资名爵周一在日内瓦车展上在欧洲推出了新款电动汽车，中国汽车制造商寻求从欧洲传统竞争对手手中夺取更多市场份额。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 11:55:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/renault-leads-europes-ev-defence-geneva-chinese-rivals-expand-2024-02-26/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：随着个人消费支出 (PCE) 的出现，蓬勃发展的股市回落</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-26/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 11:03:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>